         MACRO
&NAME    $SW24
         GBLC  &ADRMODE
         AIF   ('&ADRMODE' EQ '24').GO24
         LCLC  &IDX
&IDX     SETC  '&SYSNDX'
* MACRO TO SWITCH TO 24 BIT TEMPORARILY
&NAME    LA    R15,LA&IDX           ------->
         N     R15,=A(X'7FFFFFFF')  ×SWITCH TO 24 BIT MODE
         $BSM  0,R15                ------->
LA&IDX   DS    0H
.GO24    ANOP
         MEND
